Paper: hep-th/0102067

Date: 2001-02-13

Title: Massless particles of any spin obey linear equations of motion

Authors: Bojan Gornik, Norma Mankoc Borstnik

Comments: 11 pages, short version of hep-th/0102008

The proof is presented that the Poincare symmetry determines the equations ofmotion for massless particles of any spin in 2n-dimensional spaces, which arelinear in the momentum.